<div class="title">2C-B Revitalised My Ecstasy Experience</div>
<div class="substance">MDMA (Ecstasy) & 2C-B</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Respondent+62&Exact=1">Respondent 62</a></div>
<div class="collection">From <a href="exp_group.php?Group=Ecstasy.org">Ecstasy.org Collection</a></div>


